/**
 * HashtagNode - Custom Lexical Node for Hashtags
 *
 * Renders #tag and #[[multi word]] hashtags with:
 * - Visual styling with semantic color tokens
 * - Click handler to filter notes by tag
 * - Accessibility support
 */

